{"tid":978100,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"其實扣埋俾銀行既利息，要升幾多先賺倒錢","createTime":"2019-01-11T15:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T01:22:32.000Z","uid":38316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7120f4dbd1e0cfa4fa8caf90d72da4bca8b1693c","tid":978100,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T15:48:40.000Z","msg":"見啲人賬面有賺就當賺咗<br />\n但想知真實要升幾多先可以抵倒利息同雜費？"},{"pid":"cea167283517514485868ef91ee0d39360f5ef0a","tid":978100,"uid":13065,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T16:24:11.000Z","msg":"首先學咗點樣計一手幾錢，以股票A為例，每手1000股，股價係$13，一手價錢等於$13x1000股=$13000<br />\n假設股價上升至$14.5，每手價錢會上升至$14.5x1000股=$14500，賬面利潤$14500-$13000=$1500，扣除手續費同佣金就係實際所得，普遍嚟講銀行嘅費用會貴啲，你開個股票戶口求其買一隻就一清二楚"},{"pid":"ab63a34a91ebc1fcee4246105505cdec2edd79fa","tid":978100,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T17:28:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fabe3b22d80b5fff4fbadbccb0d503c435d94a99","tid":978100,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T17:29:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34e67a92b2393313eb716798ba8ed884e14b3c67","tid":978100,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T17:32:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"defc1f709409285837240578cd40163257638e6b","tid":978100,"uid":25758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T17:33:30.000Z","msg":"拎番出黎先叫賺到錢"},{"pid":"bc7ed06291deb56bccc84ae1a20e3c6541403519","tid":978100,"uid":169786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T17:41:08.000Z","msg":"講樓定股？"},{"pid":"a7877d11cb8585b073123a945baba84b90ef8e23","tid":978100,"uid":13065,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bc7ed06291deb56bccc84ae1a20e3c6541403519","tid":978100,"uid":169786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T17:41:08.000Z","msg":"講樓定股？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:13:00.000Z","msg":"屌係喎應該係講緊樓<img src=\"/assets/fa